<!-- ====== COMPANY OVERVIEW ====== -->
<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark">About <span class="text-danger">SGRC Consulting Services</span></h2>
            <p class="text-muted mt-3">Delivering Excellence in Power Systems, Energy Transition & Cybersecurity</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <p>
                    At <strong>SGRC Consulting Services</strong>, we bring comprehensive global experience in
                    <strong>Power System Studies</strong> and deep technical knowledge in analyzing
                    <strong>
                        shunt and series compensation, SVCs, FACTS, HVDC, synchronous condensers,
                        power plants, transmission system dynamic controls, data centers, electric vehicle
                        charging infrastructure, and cybersecurity.
                    </strong>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our consultants are proficient with leading tools including
                    <strong>Siemens PSS®E, DigSILENT PowerFactory, ETAP, PSCAD, EMTP</strong>, and
                    a range of proprietary in-house applications. We focus on the
                    <strong>planning, design, and operation</strong> of complex and interconnected power systems.
                </p>
                <p>
                    SGRC has strong expertise in <strong>voltage control and reactive power planning</strong>,
                    applying the most effective tools and procedures to ensure stability and efficiency.
                    We conduct <strong>steady-state, voltage, and transient stability studies</strong>
                    across regional transmission systems, generation interconnections, renewable integration,
                    and sub-synchronous resonance analysis.
                </p>
                <p>
                    As organizations navigate the <strong>#EnergyTransition</strong>, SGRC stands ready with
                    proven experience, cutting-edge tools, and strategic insights to support your path to a
                    sustainable <strong>#FutureOfEnergy</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

